The paper deals with the vulnerability of face recognition systems to deep morphing, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of GANs in generating deep morphs also falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the need for automated detection methods, which is related to cybersecurity (cs.CR). The experiments involve the use of neural networks, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
